  "conclusion": "The environmental block does not earn its place. Against a pooled Brier score of order 1e-02 it moves the score by order 1e-05, in both directions depending on horizon, and the enriched block did not rescue it. Substantially all of the model's skill comes from the seasonal climatology and the reporting-history block. The enriched block was therefore not shipped.",
